<p>Email wins on every metric. It costs almost nothing. It reaches more people. And it converts better because your subscribers already know your salon.</p>
<h3>Why Salons Have a Built-In Advantage</h3>
<p>Most businesses struggle to build an email list. Salons do not have that problem. Every client who books gives you their name, email, and phone number. A salon with 500 active clients already has a 500-person email list. No lead magnets needed. No opt-in funnels required.</p>
<p>The question is not whether your salon should do email marketing. The question is why you have not started yet.</p>
